verbose_text: The levels of Th1 cytokines (IL-2, IFN-gamma +) and Th2 cytokines (IL-4, IL-10) were significantly increased at both 3 dpi and 6 dpi, suggesting that the host is in an inflammatory response stage, as shown by a mixed Th1 / Th2 immune response.
